I"U<h1 id="configuration-file">Configuration File</h1>

<p>The configuration file stores the settings that have been saved on the ScummVM GUI. This is a plain text file which can be edited directly.</p>

<p>There are some <strong>advanced settings which are only available through the configuration file only.</strong></p>

